This is the Deploy agent. This daemon can be run on any linux host and will
allow Deploy to proxy connections through this host.

## Installation

Check out this code onto a server and create the following configuration files
which will be provided by Deploy.

* ca.pem - The CA certificate used to authenticate the server
* certificate.pem - The agent certificate used to authenticate this agent
* key.pem - The key corresponding to certificate.pem

Finally, execute agent.rb
